snippet.title: Amber Heard's Muscle Car Still Parked At Johnny Depp's Hollywood Hills Castle
snippet.description:
Tuesday, May 31, 2016 - Despite filing a restraining order against husband Johnny Depp last week, Amber Heard is still parking her Dodge Charger at Depp's fairy castle above the Sunset Blvd. in the Hollywood Hills.
